
# Go workspace file — a local one-module `use .` shadows any ancestor go.work on
# the dev machine so a plain `go build` resolves against this module's go.mod.
# Machine-local insulation, not source (per Go convention).
go.work
go.work.sum

# Executables
cmd/aims/aims
/aims

# Local Qubes deploy tooling (personal environment; kept out of the repo for now)
contrib/qubes/

# Claude Code local settings (per-session permission allowlist) + scratch notes.
# Machine-local tooling config, not source.
/.claude/
